Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.30,0:03:15.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How can this be?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.02,0:03:19.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My granddaughter Asseylum, assassinated,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.44,0:03:23.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and we go to war against Earth without\Nso much as a declaration?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.36,0:03:28.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Surely they knew what would come\Nof harming a goodwill ambassador.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.19,0:03:29.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Knowing that, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.03,0:03:32.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is going on there
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.99,0:03:34.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,without my knowledge?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.04,0:03:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We are told that the assassination\Nwas a terrorist act.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.41,0:03:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But does that not imply no hostile\Nintent on the part of the UE?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.33,0:03:46.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It is obvious that anti-Vers\Nfactions exist on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.55,0:03:49.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To allow this assassination\Nin spite of that
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.01,0:03:51.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,leads me to believe that her\Nsecurity was deliberately lax.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.80,0:03:54.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There is also the possibility\Nthat the assassination
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.93,0:03:57.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,was perpetrated by the UE government under\Nthe guise of a terrorist attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.31,0:03:59.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To what end?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.98,0:04:04.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Her Highness is of royal blood, one able\Nto summon forth the power of Aldnoah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.48,0:04:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That bloodline is the very foundation\Nof the Vers Empire's might.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.57,0:04:09.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is baffling.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.53,0:04:15.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Inform the UE government that we\Nare suspending hostilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.83,0:04:18.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And then uncover\Nthe truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.04,0:04:19.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.50,0:04:26.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How goes the war,\NCount Cruhteo?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.67,0:04:28.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All goes well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.34,0:04:31.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tokyo and its surrounding cities\Nhave been conquered,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.72,0:04:35.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and Shinawara, where Princess Asseylum\Nfell, is already in our hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.51,0:04:37.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well done.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.68,0:04:40.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Incidentally, where is\NSir Trillram?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.98,0:04:44.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is he still out distinguishing himself\Non the battlefield?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.73,0:04:48.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As to that... I regret to inform you\Nthat he has fallen in battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.78,0:04:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Fallen in battle?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.57,0:04:52.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is this true?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.03,0:04:54.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It is most regrettable.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.12,0:05:00.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He was caught in the meteor bombardment\Nthat some ruffian launched on my territory.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.45,0:05:02.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That is not possible...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.00,0:05:07.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Odd. I informed him\Nof the bombardment.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.21,0:05:09.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He should not have been\Ncaught in it unawares.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.96,0:05:13.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sir Trillram served me well\Nas my guest.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.34,0:05:16.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To think that he should be taken\Nfrom us in this manner...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.39,0:05:19.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We shall pray for the soul\Nof our brave warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.89,0:05:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,On that note, did anyone\Nwitness his end?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.74,0:05:34.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What should I do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.90,0:05:37.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They knew Princess Asseylum\Nwas alive, and yet...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.53,0:05:41.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I do nothing, she really will\Nbe assassinated sooner or later.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.75,0:05:43.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want it repaired immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.71,0:05:45.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just stand there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.38,0:05:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Argyre... Its head!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.72,0:05:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness you\Nare unharmed, Sir Vlad!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.80,0:06:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You call this unharmed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.72,0:06:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My honor has been tarnished!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.06,0:06:07.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Was your opponent\Nthat powerful?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.06,0:06:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No. I was made a fool of by some\Norange, impudent cur!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.86,0:06:15.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.66,0:06:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Should you not be at\Nthe Count's side?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.99,0:06:23.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was disciplined.\NFor speaking out of turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.50,0:06:25.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking out of turn?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.33,0:06:28.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I said that I wished him\Nto send me into battle, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.75,0:06:30.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're just like them, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.80,0:06:34.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're a Terran. Impudent.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.76,0:06:39.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You are that eager to distinguish\Nyourself in battle and win favor?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.59,0:06:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.90,0:06:43.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like that! I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.10,0:06:46.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Her Highness, I want to...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.19,0:06:50.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.45,0:07:01.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I get it.\NThis puts it on autopilot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.66,0:07:03.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are your names?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.54,0:07:05.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nina Klein.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.08,0:07:06.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Yutaro Tsumugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.54,0:07:08.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kisaki Matsuribi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.16,0:07:11.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, are we going to\Nbe sent into battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.75,0:07:15.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No way. These are just\Nsupplementary lessons.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.34,0:07:17.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just to cover our bases.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.05,0:07:17.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.93,0:07:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're covering their bases...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.18,0:07:25.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who drove off\Nthe enemy Kataphrakt, Amifumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.56,0:07:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Capt. Magbaredge!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.14,0:07:31.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, it was this boy\Nwho planned the operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.73,0:07:33.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Operation?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.48,0:07:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.98,0:07:39.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think it was elaborate\Nenough to call an "operation."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.07,0:07:42.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You were the pilot\Nof that trainer?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.07,0:07:44.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am. I'm Inaho Kaizuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.12,0:07:46.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kaizuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.58,0:07:50.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am. Warrant Officer\NKaizuka is my sister,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.42,0:07:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That was fine work, Inaho.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.79,0:07:58.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your efforts saved the lives of many\Nof my crew, as well as the civilians.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.21,0:08:00.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your sister must be proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.72,0:08:04.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you were enlisted, I'd be tempted\Nto put you in for commendations.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.47,0:08:09.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Commendations?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.27,0:08:10.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Medals.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.69,0:08:15.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing!\NWe could get medals!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.61,0:08:17.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing? Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.53,0:08:20.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course it is! I've never\Nseen anyone with a medal!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.95,0:08:25.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's only because nobody's seen\Nany real fighting for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.33,0:08:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Instructor Marito!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.70,0:08:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Instructor"? Does this look\Nlike a school to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.79,0:08:33.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My apologies, Lt. Marito.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.67,0:08:36.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Medals are gonna be a whole\Nlot more common soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.25,0:08:41.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're in a war. Honor is about the\Nonly reward they can hand out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.38,0:08:45.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, dying for honor\Nisn't such a bad thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.05,0:08:48.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because it's hard to survive\Nand live in misery.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.68,0:08:49.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lt. Marito.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.56,0:08:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.35,0:08:56.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hanging out your shingle\Non a military boat, Doc?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.11,0:08:58.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Those who do not work\Ndo not eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.28,0:09:04.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say that I appreciate you shattering\Nthose kids' illusions, Lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.33,0:09:14.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't hitting\Nthe bottle, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.17,0:09:16.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so touched\Nthat you trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.54,0:09:19.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you might be picking on\Nthose kids because you were drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.80,0:09:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I am under the influence.\NOf my lot in life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.14,0:09:29.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Tanegashima Report,\Nyou mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.06,0:09:34.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sins you've committed cling to\Nyour soul and haunt you forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.56,0:09:38.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And sins that have gone unpunished\Naren't forgiven until you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.03,0:09:46.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Humeray...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.99,0:09:54.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your hands are clean.\NOn the contrary, you saved his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.50,0:09:57.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that what I did?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.21,0:10:01.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.96,0:10:03.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's from Mars!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.05,0:10:05.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They say they've announced\Nan armistice!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.01,0:10:09.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Attention, foolish people of Earth.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.05,0:10:14.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rayregalia Vers Rayvers,\Nnoble emperor of the Vers Empire,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.68,0:10:19.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}has issued an armistice declaration\Nto the United Earth government.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.06,0:10:22.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}Even as we feel intense shame in\Nour common ancestry with you,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.52,0:10:24.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We can barely transmit at all... All we get\Nare these pirate broadcasts of theirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.78,0:10:27.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}our desire is that this act conveys to\Nyou, the deeply sinful people of Earth{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.32,0:10:27.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So what's this mean,\Nthe war's on hold for now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.07,0:10:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}who took the life of Her Highness\NPrincess Asseylum,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.74,0:10:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Grandfather must be trying to put a stop\Nto the knights' outrageous behavior.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.78,0:10:34.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}the profound compassion\Nof His Imperial Majesty Rayregalia.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.08,0:10:35.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The emperor of Mars?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.08,0:10:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}I repeat, Rayregalia Vers Ravers,\Nnoble emperor of the Vers Empire...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.25,0:10:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.83,0:10:42.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They say that His Imperial Majesty has issued\Nan armistice declaration to the UE government.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.46,0:10:47.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Over our heads?! Without so much\Nas a word to the Orbital Knights?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.34,0:10:51.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I must offer counsel\Nto His Majesty...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.77,0:10:55.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I shall use the\Naudience chamber!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.43,0:10:56.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Call the moon base!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.89,0:10:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Milord!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.27,0:11:04.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He was not killed in the\Nmeteor bombardment, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.32,0:11:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, Milord.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.15,0:11:09.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Nilokeras appears to have been\Ndamaged in battle and then deserted.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.74,0:11:13.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There is someone whose actions\NI wish to look into.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.95,0:11:17.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Infiltrate Castle Cruhteo\Nand continue your investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.91,0:11:18.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes, Milord!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.35,0:11:42.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They open hostilities without warning\Nand then stop just as abruptly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.19,0:11:44.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This whole thing doesn't\Nmake any sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.07,0:11:48.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you suppose that means the enemy\Nisn't monolithic, either?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.74,0:11:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Has anyone tried\Nto contact us?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.49,0:11:53.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, ma'am. The jamming\Nis still too strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.91,0:11:59.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going, Milady?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.42,0:12:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To speak with\Nthis ship's master.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.29,0:12:05.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I shall tell her\Nwho I really am.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.13,0:12:07.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Princess, you-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.55,0:12:14.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And then I shall have her\Ninform Vers of my safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.55,0:12:17.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Doing so will end this war.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.06,0:12:21.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's too dangerous! The rebels will come\Nfor you before word reaches His Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.69,0:12:25.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Which is exactly why this armistice\Nprovides us with the perfect opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.44,0:12:27.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.32,0:12:33.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They aren't the sort to obey\Nthe terms of an armistice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.57,0:12:35.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'll just get yourself crushed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.12,0:12:39.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But the longer this war drags on,\Nthe more casualties there will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.91,0:12:42.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to die,\Nthat's your decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.87,0:12:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But leave me out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.13,0:12:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,An attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.18,0:12:53.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But there's an armistice!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.85,0:13:04.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It simply won't do\Nfor the war to end
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.45,0:13:06.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,without me having a chance\Nto redeem my honor!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.86,0:13:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard... He wants revenge?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.03,0:13:11.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant! Where are you going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.99,0:13:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Launch Kataphrakts! Intercept!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.28,0:13:17.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, I suggest\Nrelocating to CIC.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.70,0:13:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.66,0:13:24.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Unacceptable!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.79,0:13:27.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is His Majesty thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.79,0:13:30.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,His own flesh and blood\Nwas killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.09,0:13:33.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Assemble a fact-finding mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.18,0:13:38.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As per His Majesty's orders, we shall uncover\Nthe details of the Princess' assassination!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.97,0:13:40.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Milord!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.53,0:13:54.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can... I can use this\Nto speak to His Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.46,0:14:10.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back on-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.96,0:14:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come! Let us pick up\Nwhere we left off!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.72,0:14:18.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Draw sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.99,0:14:39.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Aldaniti Platoon, prepare for launch.\NRaising elevator #2.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.87,0:14:44.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All units, don't use HE rounds.\NEngage using AP rounds.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.37,0:15:24.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.42,0:15:25.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.21,0:15:30.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's using the bridge\Nas a shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.88,0:15:34.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nao!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.34,0:15:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Draw sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.84,0:15:40.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?\NCome down from there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.59,0:15:42.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I could say the same to you, Yuki.\NYou're injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.55,0:15:44.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We're short on pilots!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.72,0:15:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then it'll be just as good\Nif I go out instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.31,0:15:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where are my pajamas?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.39,0:15:51.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The ones with the patches.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.41,0:16:09.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.75,0:16:16.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.59,0:16:19.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Slaine Troyard, Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.30,0:16:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Slaine? Ah, it has been\Na long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.76,0:16:25.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It has, Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.68,0:16:29.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is the purpose\Nof this visit?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.52,0:16:32.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There is a matter that I must\Ninform you of, Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.27,0:16:38.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is, Princess\NAsseylum is alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.11,0:16:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have seen her\Nwith my own two eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.62,0:16:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was the Orbital Knights who made the attempt\Non her life in their lust for war with Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.70,0:16:52.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But their attempt failed,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.75,0:16:57.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and Princess Asseylum is alive\Nsomewhere on Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.43,0:17:05.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, you show yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.39,0:17:07.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,my nemesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.61,0:17:18.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A trainer?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.15,0:17:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe it, is that-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.98,0:17:20.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Inaho?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.69,0:17:23.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A tactical suit isn't gonna\Nprotect you against that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.49,0:17:27.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There is no armor my blades\Ncannot slice through!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.16,0:17:30.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This will be over\Nin an instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.84,0:17:41.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Inaho!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.43,0:17:53.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.31,0:18:00.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Reactive armor. Armor plates\Nthat are made of explosives.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.48,0:18:04.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They were originally designed to detonate\Nand deflect incoming enemy fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.70,0:18:05.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.95,0:18:12.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's using the blasts to disperse\Nthe blade's plasma?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.96,0:18:17.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Control! Tilt the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.13,0:18:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mizusaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.00,0:18:20.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Flood ballast!\NOpen well dock hatch!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.14,0:18:32.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Unhand me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.31,0:18:37.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be glad to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.36,0:18:48.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Backpack dumped.\NBailing out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.74,0:18:51.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What the-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.34,0:19:04.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Inaho!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.00,0:19:05.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What just happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.59,0:19:08.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Steam explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.64,0:19:13.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The massive amount of thermal energy in those\Nblades flashed the seawater to steam
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.02,0:19:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and the impact from the high\Npressure steam destroyed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.73,0:19:26.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Inaho Kaizuka... He hardly\Nseems like a student, does he?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.24,0:19:29.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, ma'am. He's a surprisingly\Nuseful boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.32,0:19:34.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mizusaki. Shall I tell you\Nwhy you can't get a date?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.45,0:19:38.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't partners prefer\Na forthright personality?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.42,0:19:42.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yours isn't forthright.\NIt's unfiltered.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.88,0:19:49.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go pick him up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.04,0:20:22.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If what you say is true,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.88,0:20:25.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,it is most regrettable indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.59,0:20:28.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I beg you, Majesty, please stop\Nthis war without delay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.21,0:20:31.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And please rescue\NPrincess Asseylum.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.97,0:20:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I shall see to it at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.43,0:20:39.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Your Majesty.\NI shall take my leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.69,0:20:49.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It is exactly as you said,\NCount Saazbaum.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.28,0:20:54.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Terrans are not\Nto be trusted.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.24,0:20:57.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They have spies everywhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.99,0:21:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and are scheming to overthrow Vers if\Nthe opportunity should present itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.50,0:21:05.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It is scandalous that they would try\Nto deceive Your Majesty with lies!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.59,0:21:08.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You, whose heart is grieving the\Nloss of your beloved princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.67,0:21:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My Emperor.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.42,0:21:15.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I ask that you smite this foul race\Nwith the iron fist of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.94,0:21:31.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In the name of Rayregalia Vers\NRayvers, Emperor of Vers,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.61,0:21:35.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I hereby renew my\Ndeclaration of war.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.49,0:21:37.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Attack the Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.16,0:21:40.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Those who would do harm\Nto my flesh and blood...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.91,0:21:43.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...must burn!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.13,0:21:53.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Slaine Troyard, you mean\Nharm to our cause...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.18,0:21:57.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How ironic...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.68,0:22:03.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is it not, Dr. Troyard?
